Package domain

Class ItemType

java.lang.Object
domain.ItemType
public class ItemType extends Object
Class Type of Item. This class represents a type of item with a specified number of attributes. the maximum number of objects of this class is one.

  • Field Details

    • nameType

      private String nameType
      Non static attribute nameType. Default value to "". This attribute specifies the type of item of a set of items, like "films", "videogames"...

    • nameAttributes

      private ArrayList<String> nameAttributes
      Non static attribute nameAttributes. Default value to new ArrayList<>(). Names of the different characteristics or attributes of a type of items. This attribute can be {duration,genre,description}, or {colour, size, price, duration}.
